import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Row, Col, InputGroup } from "react-bootstrap"
import './Registration.css'

function Registration ({handleChange, formInputData, handleSubmit}) {

    return (
        <Row className='form-row row'>
            <Col className='col'>
                <InputGroup.Text type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.firstName} name='firstName' className='form-control' placeholder='First Name' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.lasstName} name='lastName' className='form-control' placeholder='Last Name' />
                <input type='number' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.npi} name='npi' className='form-control' placeholder='NPI #' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.phone} name='phone' className='form-control' placeholder='Phone Numbewr' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.email} name='email' className='form-control' placeholder='Email Address' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.streetAddress} name='streetAddress' className='form-control' placeholder='Street Address' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.city} name='city' className='form-control' placeholder='City' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.state} name='state' className='form-control' placeholder='State' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.zip} name='zip' className='form-control' placeholder='Zip Code' />
                <input type='text' onChange={handleChange} value={formInputData.country} name='country' className='form-control' placeholder='Country' />
                <input type='submit' onClick={handleSubmit} className='btn-primary' />
            </Col>
        </Row>
    )
}

export default Registration;
